		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+0" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Look for what scientists know for sure, not what they assume to be true, or think may probably be true.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
